text.paragraph:
Because methimazole may cause hypoprothrombinemia and bleeding, prothrombin time should be monitored during therapy with the drug, especially before surgical procedures (see General under 
                              PRECAUTIONS
                           ).

(See 
                              WARNINGS
                           )

The drug appears in human breast milk and its use is contraindicated in nursing mothers (see 
                              WARNINGS

                           ).

(See 
                              DOSAGE AND ADMINISTRATION
                           )
